=\"background-origin: padding-box;\"><span style=\"background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"padding: 0in; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: black;\"><span arial=\"\" style=\"font-family:;\"><font size=\"3\">SBS News đã liên lạc với Bộ Nội vụ để hỏi về vấn đề này.</font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-position: 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 17.85pt;\"><span style=\"word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: scroll;\"><span style=\"background-size: auto;\"><span style=\"background-origin: padding-box;\"><span style=\"background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"background-position: 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: scroll;\"><span style=\"background-size: auto;\"><span style=\"background-origin: padding-box;\"><span style=\"background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"padding: 0in; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: black;\"><span arial=\"\" style=\"font-family:;\"><font size=\"3\">Phát ngôn nhân Bộ Nội vụ cho biết &ldquo;để duy trì tính hợp nhất cho bài thi quốc tịch, mọi câu hỏi và câu trả lời phải được bảo mật. Sẽ không phù hợp cho Bộ Nội vụ nếu có nhận định thêm về nội dung <span style=\"padding: 0in; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: blue;\"><span arial=\"\" style=\"font-family:;\">bài thi quốc tịch</span></span><span style=\"padding: 0in; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: black;\"><span arial=\"\" style=\"font-family:;\">.&rdquo;</span></span></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-position: 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 17.85pt;\"><span style=\"word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: scroll;\"><span style=\"background-size: auto;\"><span style=\"background-origin: padding-box;\"><span style=\"background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"padding: 0in; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: black;\"><span arial=\"\" style=\"font-family:;\"><span style=\"word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"float: none;\"><span style=\"orphans: 2;\"><font size=\"3\">SBS News cũng hỏi Bộ Nội vụ có bao nhiêu người trượt bài thi quốc tịch</font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"background-position: 0% 0%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 17.85pt;\"><span style=\"word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"orphans: 2;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: scroll;\"><span style=\"background-size: auto;\"><span style=\"background-origin: padding-box;\"><span style=\"background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"padding: 0in; border: 1pt windowtext; border-image: none; color: black;\"><span arial=\"\" style=\"font-family:;\"><span style=\"word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"float: none;\"><span style=\"orphans: 2;\"><font size=\"3\">&ldquo;Đối với những người dự thi trong thời gian 1/7/ 2017 đến 30/4/2018, tỷ lệ trượt là 2,9%.&rdquo;</font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; text-align: right;\">\r\n	<font color=\"#000000\"><font face=\"Times